\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528219\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528219\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hhz1665703258861.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hhz1665703258861.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hhz1665703258861.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hhz1665703258861\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">For applications deployed on Windows, specifies whether the native online help is HTML-based or WinHelp.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__topic_d144992e1_d144993e1_d144994e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__p_d144995e1_d144996e1_d144997e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">HtmlHelp</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__section_w2947ab1b5b3_w2948ab1b5_w2949ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__table_d17645e1_d17646e1_d17647e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"igs1665702672514.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/igs1665702672514.html\" title=\"The [help] section of the initialization file specifies the files to be used when online help is requested by the help ProcScript statement from a Uniface application, or within displayed messages.\">[help]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__section_msz_xvd_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d617682e114\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The ProcScript <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> statement is used to call online help, either in\n            the form of Uniface help texts or HTML files. By default, Uniface opens the default Web\n            browser and tries to load the named help topic with an <span class=\"ph filepath\">.htm</span>\n            extension. If the files does not exist, it retries with an <span class=\"ph filepath\">.html</span>\n            extension.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">HtmlHelp</span> is set to false, it looks for files with the\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">.hlp</span> extension for the now-obsolete Windows help format.</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__example_gwc_bwd_xvb\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__pre_hwc_bwd_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[help]\nHtmlHelp=TRUE</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__p_d145007e1_d145008e1_d145009e1\">Given the following ProcScript, Uniface first looks\n            for the file <span class=\"ph filepath\">UUEXTN20.HTM</span>. If it does not find it, it looks for\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">UUEXTN20.HTML</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hhz1665703258861__pre_iwc_bwd_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">help /topic \"UUEXTN20\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zks1720074466587.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>help</a><p>Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528219\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528219\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "HtmlHelp Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 For applications deployed on Windows, specifies whether the native online help is HTML-based or WinHelp. HtmlHelp = TRUE | FALSE Default value: TRUE File section: [help] Description The ProcScript help statement is used to call online help, either in the form of Uniface help texts or HTML files. By default, Uniface opens the default Web browser and tries to load the named help topic with an .htm extension. If the files does not exist, it retries with an .html extension. If HtmlHelp is set to false, it looks for files with the .hlp extension for the now-obsolete Windows help format. [help] HtmlHelp=TRUE Copy Given the following ProcScript, Uniface first looks for the file UUEXTN20.HTM . If it does not find it, it looks for UUEXTN20.HTML . help /topic \"UUEXTN20\" Copy Related Links help Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}